        <updateDate>2011-08-12T21:45:43Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Child Tax Credit Equality for Puerto Rico Act of 2011 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to make residents of Puerto Rico with less than three children&nbsp;eligible for the refundable portion of the child tax credit. Requires a phase-in of the full credit amount between 2011 and 2015.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
